timing_extrac...s_nochange_arc(25.10)    timing_extrac...s_nochange_arc(25.10)

Name
       timing_extract_model_gating_as_nochange_arc

Syntax
       timing_extract_model_gating_as_nochange_arc

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       Controls the conversion of clock gating checks to nochange arcs.

       When  set  to  false,  the software disables conversion of clock gating
       checks to nochange arcs in the extracted timing model.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

